e":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T08:43:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我聽日都去sydney<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> plan咗去fish mkt同sherlock exhibition</blockquote><br />\nFISH MARKET其實都比人食到貴哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔覺得有咩特別...<br />\n但有種蝦叫scampi , 有大隻有細隻...可以生食!<br />\n你可以試下, 好撚鮮甜...勁正..前日先食完<br />\n買左2隻細SIZE, AUD 5.1...30蚊HKD2隻<br />\n有機會試下...當然如果BUDGET多D就買大隻啦....<br />\n提提你最好帶埋濕紙巾同膠布去...<br />\n我開蝦吉到爆哂血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63fb785a882006c1c885c3d8cacad15b4231a23a","tid":259513,"uid":73311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T08:43:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Blue mountain</blockquote><br />\n去左...好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e9fd69e82f8627ef71393c46a37e313ea8942a1","tid":259513,"uid":3724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T08:45:08.000Z","msg":"Darling harbour"},{"pid":"544342cfcc17ccaa83e1576d35e37d62a99d98d5","tid":259513,"uid":73311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T09:04:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Darling harbour</blockquote><br />\n去左啦....日日食完LUNCH都行過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fed20620923b2ca244279d0a3080aed89056e6f","tid":259513,"uid":44559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T13:17:27.000Z","msg":"除左市區，一係去沙灣<br />\n<br />\n一係去藍山<br />\n<br />\n夜晚去new Town 飲野"},{"pid":"47971f139daa1e438a96d3c0ba732d1659c06f93","tid":259513,"uid":73311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T08:38:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>除左市區，一係去沙灣<br />\n<br />\n一係去藍山<br />\n<br />\n夜晚去new Town 飲野</blockquote><br />\n我自己一個去左藍山同行NEW TOWN<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nNEW TOWN係好多BAR既...但自己飲好無引"},{"pid":"db078ecc51c868dd6afcac0f1a53c00b5fbc9f22","tid":259513,"uid":102580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T13:58:44.000Z","msg":"去下surry hills個頭都唔錯<br />\n<br />\nbarangaroo 都好"},{"pid":"2813357b92ed65cb5812ac29fe2fe87ea6ac50be","tid":259513,"uid":73311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T16:33:12.000Z","msg":"再推下....悉尼仲有咩地方值得去?<br />\n去左<br />\nBlue Mountain National Park<br />\nBondi Beach<br />\nNew Town<br />\nSydney Opera House<br />\nDarling Harbour<br />\nFish Market<br />\nCircular Quay<br />\nThe Rocks<br />\n<br />\n未去因為無車<br />\nHunter Valley<br />\nPart Stephens<br />\n<br />\n打算去<br />\nArt Gallery of NSW<br />\nTaronga Zoo<br />\nNewcastle<br />\n<br />\n我計過仲有好多日無野做....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人有好推薦?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n岩玩可以一齊去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}